            </div>
            
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-8">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-md bg-muted/50 hover:bg-muted transition-colors">
                        <div class="text-2xl">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
